    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Does not that imply your determination not to allow a permit to a Member of this House, if possible</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-251c86b7-7630-4616-8a84-a5bb3f5dcf3f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
