                The Prime Minister
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-a3d70ff8-9484-4e18-a036-80c420a92811" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1941-10-21/debates/978a41b4-96f3-46a8-873a-202dd2eb42fc/MembersOfParliament(VisitsToIreland)#contribution-a3d70ff8-9484-4e18-a036-80c420a92811">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
