<p class="">The interruption has not illumined the Debate. [<em>Interruption</em>.] We have suffered at the hands of too many of you "Yes-men" in this House. Let us get on with the discussion. [<em>Interruption</em>.]</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
